{"tid":1637623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[遍地開花之東京要人] 1013促日發聲大遊行","createTime":"2019-10-08T04:52:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T14:47:41.000Z","uid":74888,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1c1aa7f12eac93f9b8fecf7f3bdccecf74d699a8","tid":1637623,"uid":74888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:52:51.000Z","msg":"各位在日既巴絲打!呢幾日香港發生咁多事,相信大家既心亦都唔好受<br />\n機會黎啦, 係日本既你地係時候話比香港既手足知,我地冇放棄香港冇放棄你地!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n繼上次賀佢老母之後, 今次又有新活動<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><em>上次有好多地方都做得唔好, 望大家多多見諒。</em></span><br />\n<br />\n今次已向日本警方申請及已獲得日方既不反對通知書, 所以大家可以唔洗心掛掛咁參加今次既EVENT<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n是次活動有可能會有記者, 所以如果大家唔想上鏡的話請包得實啲<br />\n<br />\n<strong>主題: </strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">【1013促日發聲大遊行】</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">捍人權・責警黑・裁官暴<br />\n懇請日本捍人權，譴責制裁港警官</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">日期：10月13日（日）<br />\n集合：16:30 日比谷公園霞門<br />\n出發：17:00-18:00<br />\n路線：日比谷公園&rarr;外務省&rarr;日比谷公園<br />\n裝備：全黑服裝、口罩/豬咀、其他如頭盔及鐳射筆等申請中</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><em>*已向日本警方申請，已獲日本警方不反 (updated at 10/7)*</em></span><br />\n<br />\n有任何最新消息及改動將會於公海公告, 未必會係POST UPDATE, 所以詳情請留意返公海<br />\nTG公海：<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/N6og8RXQ1SqM3RgG8VKuUw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FN6og8RXQ1SqM3RgG8VKuUw&d=nKAZF5zAPcG2WvBXR7hnIhV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=2bc5e6c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/N6og8RXQ1SqM3RgG8VKuUw</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KBmkjqY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKBmkjqY.png&h=550f8362&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FZgDQxD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFZgDQxD.jpg&h=5531f68e&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/smTreZj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://